Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.35,0:00:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们毁灭你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.83,0:00:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 雷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让沙布拉尼古鲁复活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了打开自己的双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜重蹈覆辙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是迟早的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔王的灵魂正在聚集力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.09,0:00:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备再次吞噬我的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.85,0:00:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.69,0:00:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说 你并非为了向我们复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是为了封印自己体内的魔王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.16,0:00:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定把命运托付给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.75,0:00:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有丝毫的犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.39,0:00:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于又一次见到了光明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.72,0:00:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷藏 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.43,0:01:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次毁灭魔王吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.49,0:01:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜…托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.06,0:01:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷藏 雷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 波克塔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭吧 魔王的亡魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰洛士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了个很长很长的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚无之梦 毁灭之梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在混沌黑暗外的空虚之梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.62,0:02:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰洛士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.91,0:02:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为在雷藏灵魂被吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:02:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔王觉醒的那一瞬间可以得手的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:02:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到能再次复活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也梦到和尔等的重逢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可从未如此想过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个眼神的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丝毫不绝望的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个光芒正是我噩梦的源头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:04:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero hour 走向毁灭之物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰洛士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带大家来到这里已经是耗尽全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰洛士 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为现在可不能失去莉娜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了消灭魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 应该说是魔王的亡魂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔王的亡魂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那并非是曾经和莉娜战斗过的魔王本体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思 这并不是完整的魔王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得魔王加布吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加布
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加布是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.74,0:04:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 好像在哪儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:05:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加布以不同于普通的形式复活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因而成为了我们魔族的叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以原本不存在的形式复活的魔王又如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法想象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过对我们魔族而言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法对其置之不理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处理掉魔王的亡魂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是赋予你的使命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果莉娜现在被杀掉的话 我可就头疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是亡魂 魔王始终是魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想毁灭它的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.08,0:05:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重破斩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重破斩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指过去打倒过沙布拉尼古鲁的咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.31,0:05:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那种咒文的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不早点使用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说得那么轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那道咒文犹如赌博一般
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是能将此世毁灭的禁断招数
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能说用就用的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对战沙那法时就用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不便细说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之 各位快去避难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 快点逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽量逃远些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要舍弃这个好不容易复兴的国家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然明白你们的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.99,0:06:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但此刻…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.97,0:06:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国家是指住在这里的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要人民存在 国家无论多少次都会复兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 说的不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把大家带去安全的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人民才是国家 你说得太对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是别人教我的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快点把大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我经历毁灭之梦的人们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起走向毁灭之路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔夫拉希亚的各位 快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:07:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波赛路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 那家伙不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 塔夫拉希亚王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的并非是波赛路王子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边不是波赛路又是何人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 快点逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有生命的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部走向毁灭之路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒灵四王缚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的咒文这样已经是极限了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不畏绝望之人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:09:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与吾同行 共迈毁灭之路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭吧 毁灭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝毁灭 渴望混沌的人们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.95,0:10:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何要反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何要拒绝这迟早降临的沉睡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.39,0:10:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.49,0:10:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是沙布拉尼古鲁的毁灭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能起作用的 只是高里的光之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好动手了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.11,0:10:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.53,0:10:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔夫拉希亚好不容易才走上复兴之路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:11:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能甘心就此打住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波克塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家被疫病袭击时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被沉睡的封印覆盖时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.65,0:11:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…都从未放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能就此打住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比黄昏还要昏暗者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比血液还要鲜红者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在时间之流中出现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以汝之伟名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾于此黑暗起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.71,0:11:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 波克塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的 龙破斩是借用沙布拉尼古鲁力量的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻挡在吾等前方所有的愚蠢之物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合吾等之力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐与其平等的毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙破斩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都给我从这里消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借用魔王力量的龙破斩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:12:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明对其无法生效的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙 没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 龙破斩并非无用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比黄昏还要昏暗者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比血液还要鲜红者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.02,0:12:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在时间之流中出现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以汝之伟名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾于此黑暗起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻挡在吾等前方所有的愚蠢之物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合吾等之力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐与其平等的毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙破斩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.27,0:12:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙破斩是借用沙布拉尼古鲁力量的咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够强制抽出他的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强制抽出力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些无数的未知怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是魔王本体的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些本体力量被龙破斩强制的作为力量抵消了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以无法保持原形
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和波克塔用龙破斩一路打过去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀出一条血路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能顺利进入
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会用神灭斩全力进攻的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比黄昏还要昏暗者…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.43,0:13:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩灵裂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙破斩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙破斩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙破斩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙破斩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙破斩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙破斩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 莉娜的魔力消耗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法接近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神灭斩使用不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.01,0:14:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做的 这有这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渴望毁灭之人为何要去保护
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们渴望的东西 是自己的意识和力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们渴望的毁灭 是靠自己的意识和力量达成的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连这些都忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵王结魔弹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这起 你一步都休想前行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.49,0:15:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿梅莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.17,0:15:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿梅莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿梅莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有用重破斩了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…使用过一次才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个咒文是多么的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷入混沌之海的那股恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求救不能 伸手不见五指的无尽黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的灵魂在沉落
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.67,0:16:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失手的话 会让大家遭受同样的遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.24,0:16:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰路刚帝士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来没觉得被雷藏改造过的身体是这么好的一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时 为救高里而使用了那个咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这次混沌的漩涡会把大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.21,0:16:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有能力却想毫无作为就结束吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次 我一定会尽我所能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.47,0:16:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波克塔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 把我送到那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此 剩下的就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波克塔 你想…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撑住啊 光之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜 别犹豫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要做好自己相信的事就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.91,0:17:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不会抱怨的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻我能做的 只有这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的性命 交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.09,0:17:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统御四界黑暗之王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依循汝之碎片之缘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以汝之力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐予吾更强的魔力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢啊 愚蠢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好把身体给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我也没指望要回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不能再让你肆意妄为了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.56,0:18:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是渺小的人类 也会努力活着的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想肆意毁灭 怎能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波克塔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波克塔制造的这次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.23,0:18:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能错过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比黑暗还要漆黑者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比夜晚还要深沉者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于混沌之海中的飘荡者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金色的黑暗之王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.17,0:18:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾与此向汝祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.46,0:18:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾与此向汝起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻挡在吾等前方所有的愚蠢之物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合吾等之力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐与其平等的毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会白费的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有着金色噩梦之人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.77,0:19:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起毁灭 去做同样的虚无之梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多点 力量再来多点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重破斩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被毁灭者击败了毁灭者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无愧于slayers之名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭吧 魔王的亡魂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波克塔 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时 波克塔打破了自己的冥王之壶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.41,0:20:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到了本体中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.36,0:20:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 波克塔他…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的灵魂如果和魔王的灵魂火拼的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 今后明明还要重建塔夫拉希亚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.49,0:20:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是一点点来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…居然还活着 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说为什么嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.37,0:21:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你要留下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.13,0:21:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.26,0:21:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么“差不多就是这样”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏我还伤感了一番
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.39,0:21:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波克塔 你要负责的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.68,0:21:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负什么责啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱说 你这个飞机场
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那边去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.01,0:21:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波赛路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.76,0:21:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看眼睛就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.82,0:21:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的儿子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.75,0:21:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.17,0:21:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父子真是好东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.15,0:21:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.22,0:22:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么关于雷藏…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罢了 他的事就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.46,0:22:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜也思乡了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.79,0:22:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在回家为时过早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.78,0:22:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要继续去寻找高里的剑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.98,0:22:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.29,0:22:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 马上出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.15,0:22:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点的话 就不管你们了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

